---
title: Chipotle Beef Meatballs & Brown Rice with Caramelised Onion, Cucumber Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Meatballs and brown rice, what a bowl of fun! Roll the meatballs up with a chipotle sauce and cook them to perfection.
The brown rice provides an extra burst of flavour to the meal and cooled down with a cucumber salsa, this dish is full of
entertainment for your tastebuds.
